  <a name="yale-university-s-equal-opportunity-and-nondiscrimination-statement"></a>
  



      <div id="mmi-23517" class="scrolling-text-module colspan-4 rag measurable magic-module" data-event-category="magic_module/scrolling_text_module/23517" data-event-label="Scrolling Text Module YALE UNIVERSITY’S Equal Opportunity and Nondiscrimination Statement (8/11)" data-instance-id="23517" data-id="107829">                  <div class="scrolling-text-module__inner" style="max-height: 36.0em" tabindex="0">
    <h4 class="scrolling-text-module__title page-title--prominence-4">YALE UNIVERSITY’S Equal Opportunity and Nondiscrimination Statement</h4>
    <p>The university is committed to basing judgments concerning the admission, education, and employment of individuals upon their qualifications and abilities and seeks to attract to its faculty, staff, and student body qualified persons from a broad range of backgrounds and perspectives.</p>

<p>Please visit Yale University’s website <a href="https://www.yale.edu/eeo-nondiscriminationstatement">at this link</a> for full information. </p>

</div>

